Ah, I had a paper round when I was 14.

16
00:00:40,079 --> 00:00:41,920
A paper round is a job.

17
00:00:41,920 --> 00:00:45,439
The job of delivering newspapers to people's homes.

18
00:00:45,439 --> 00:00:47,519
It's often done by teenagers.

19
00:00:47,519 --> 00:00:49,920
14 seems very young to be at work.

20
00:00:50,399 --> 00:00:52,560
And that's the topic of this 6 Minute English.

21
00:00:52,560 --> 00:00:54,960
Should school children have jobs?

22
