I ask this.

88
00:04:34,160 --> 00:04:38,319
What is the youngest age at which children are allowed to work in the UK?

89
00:04:38,319 --> 00:04:42,160
Is it A 12, B 13 or C 14?

90
00:04:42,240 --> 00:04:44,000
And I said C 14.

91
00:04:44,000 --> 00:04:46,000
And I'm afraid you are wrong.

92
00:04:46,000 --> 00:04:47,040
No.

93
00:04:47,040 --> 00:04:50,160
You're allowed to work from the age of 13 in the UK.

94
00:04:50,160 --> 00:04:53,439
Exceptions to this rule include TV, theatre and modelling.

95
00:04:53,439 --> 00:04:54,080
Oh, well.

96
00:04:54,080 --> 00:04:56,080
I guess I should have spent more time at school.

97
00:04:56,640 --> 00:04:58,800
Shall we have a recap of the vocabulary?

98
00:04:58,800 --> 00:05:00,800
