Big money back in the 80s.

102
00:05:08,879 --> 00:05:11,760
Did you supplement your earnings with a Saturday job?

103
00:05:11,759 --> 00:05:12,319
I did.

104
00:05:12,319 --> 00:05:16,480
I had a Saturday job in a supermarket and also in a fishing chip shop.

105
00:05:16,480 --> 00:05:18,399
But it wasn't always on a Saturday.

106
